<div id="full">
<ul>
<br>Text 2 Mind Map is a web application that converts texts to mind maps. <br>
It takes a structured list of words or sentences, interprets it, <br>
and draws a mind map out of them. Try it out above!<br><br>
</ul>

<h2>&nbsp;Hints</h2>
<ul>
<li><b>Switch to fullscreen</b> if your mind map has many nodes and barely fits.
<li>Tick the <b>"freeze map"</b>-checkbox to make the layout sticky, then drag the nodes around to rearrange the layout.
<li>Place only one word at the first indent level. This word will be placed as center of your mind map.
<br><br>
Text2MindMap is a work in progress, feedback is appreciated.<br>
Good? Bad? Problems? Comments? Tell us!
